javac.file

类 Locations

  • java.lang.Object
    • javac.file.Locations

  • public class Locations
extends java.lang.Object
    This class converts command line arguments, environment variables and system properties (in File.pathSeparator-separated String form) into a boot class path, user class path, and source path (in Collection<String> form).

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

        public static java.net.URL[] pathToURLs(java.lang.String path)
        Utility method for converting a search path string to an array of directory and JAR file URLs. Note that this method is called by apt and the DocletInvoker.
        参数:
        path - the search path string
        返回:
        the resulting array of directory and JAR file URLs
